<PB N="16" REF="007923_0015_102E023BC25E0C70">
<HEAD><HI>At a</HI> CONFERENCE <HI>with the</HI> Indians, <HI>held at</HI> Ea&s;ton, <HI>on</HI> Monday, <HI>the 8th of</HI> November, 1756.</HEAD>
<P>PRESENT,
<LIST>
<ITEM><HI>The Honourable</HI> WILLIAM DENNY, <HI><ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> Lieutenant-Governor.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><LIST>
