<ITEM>JOSEPH FOX,</ITEM>
<ITEM>WILLIAM MASTERS,</ITEM>
<ITEM>JOHN HUGHES,</ITEM>
</LIST></ITEM>
<ITEM>TEEDYUSCUNG, <HI>the</HI> Delaware <HI>King, Speaker of the</HI> Six Nations,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Delaware Indians,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Shawane&s;e,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Mohiccons,</ITEM>
<ITEM>PUMPSHIRE, <HI>a</HI> Jer&s;ey Delaware In|dian, <HI>Interpreter.</HI></ITEM>
