</LIST></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Lieutenant</HI> M'ALPIN, <HI>and En&s;ign</HI> JEFFRYS, <HI>Recruiting Officers, of the</HI> Royal <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"></ITEM>
